            . I am the wife of Joseph Goodwin- we live in <placeName id="t18260914-282-crimeloc1602">Cow-cross-street, Smithfield</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18260914-282-crimeloc1602" type="placeName" value="Cow-cross-street, Smithfield"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18260914-282-crimeloc1602" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260914-282-off1600 t18260914-282-crimeloc1602"></join>, and <rs id="t18260914-282-viclabel1603" type="occupation">keep a grocer's shop</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260914-282-victim1539 t18260914-282-viclabel1603"></join>. On the 8th of September this cap was safe when the prisoner came into my shop to offer me a large baking dish to sell; I told her I did not want it; she pressed hard for me to buy it, and put it on the counter; I laid the cap down, she took it up, and said "Very well, it is of no use to buy if you don't want it;" she went out; I ran after her - she was taken, but had not the cap then.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260914-282-person1541">
                  BENJAMIN 
                  PHILLIPS
               <interp inst="t18260914-282-person1541" type="surname" value="PHILLIPS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260914-282-person1541" type="given" value="BENJAMIN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260914-282-person1541" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. I saw the prisoner come out of the shop with the dish in her hand; she walked at a quick pace; the prosecutor came out, and called "Stop that woman" - she turned into a lane; I pursued and took her - she had several persons round her, who said "Go the watch-house" - no cap was found on her.</p>
               <p>JURY. Q. Were you the first person who took her? A. Yes; she said I might search her, but I should find no cap on her, but she was in a crowd, and, to the best of my belief, it had been given to another person.</p>
